name: Worlokk of the Void

The Worlokk of the Void: In the world of Geoda, walks a mysterious Worlokk who controls the life fabric, the essence that connects the space with the physical world. The Worlokk neither speaks or sleeps but only wanders, looking for three other mysterious beings for reasons only known to themself.
